      <section role="ITEM">
        <title>File Upload Details</title>

        <para role="TEXT">In this section of the form, you can specify files to upload,
        containing any documents that you want to attach or that the Issuing
        Bank has requested.</para>

        <para role="TEXT">Click <guibutton>Add a file</guibutton> to display a dialogue
        box where you can browse to a file on your disk and upload it.</para>

        <para role="TEXT">The section starts with a list of files you have uploaded, or
        with the text <guilabel>No files (Maximum 5)</guilabel>. Click the
        <guiicon>Delete</guiicon> <inlinemediaobject>
            <imageobject>
              <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_trash.gif" role="ICON_TRASH"
                         width="4mm" />
            </imageobject>
          </inlinemediaobject> icon next to an item in the list to delete
        it.</para>
